results.name: Shifts left by 2 places under series reversion.
comment: Series reversion of the g.f. gives the same sequence with two initial terms (1, 1) dropped.
formula: G.f. satisfies A((A(x) - x - x^2)/x^2) = x.
mathematica: Nest[InverseSeries[#] x^2 + x^2 + x &, x + O[x]^2, 14][[3]]
results.author: _Vladimir Reshetnikov_, Aug 07 2019
